Package com.lucaskjaerozhang.wikitext_parser.grammar

Interface WikiTextListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
WikiTextBaseListener
public interface WikiTextListener extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by WikiTextParser.
